meanings: (재산·목숨·나라 등을) guard, (방어하다) defend, protect, (보호하다) look after, take care of
(약속·법·질서 등을) keep, obey, follow, observe, stick[adhere] to, uphold
부탁 This is a public place. Have some manners.
부탁 Please be at your best behavior.
유제품에 관해서 The lactic acid bacillus in yoghurt keeps your intestines healthy.
